{
  "id": "adv_main_01_12_02",
  "title": "星見編3章7話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshimi-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃と俺が寮に戻ると）\n（みんなは明日の予定を確認している最中だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When Kotono and I return to the dorm‚)\n(everyone is going over tomorrow’s itinerary.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "なかなか確定しなかった\nグランプリのタイムスケジュールですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We weren’t able to pin down\nthe Grand Prix schedule before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "最終的には、私達月のテンペストと\n対戦相手のステージが明日のラスト",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but in the end‚ it was officially determined that Moon Tempest\nand our competitor will be the final performance tomorrow‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん達サニーピースの出番は\n明後日ということで正式決定しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and Sakura’s team‚ Sunny Peace‚\nwill perform the day after tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "気を揉ませるなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh‚ the suspense!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "その分、お化粧する時間がじっくり出来て\n良かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This will give you that much more time to fix your makeup.\nI’m happy for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.63337869644165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "余計こと言わなくていい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for your unsolicited opinion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.066712029774983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……時間がはっきりしないなんて\n珍しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ why aren’t the times set in stone?\nThat’s unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.689478421211234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "それだけグランプリが\n盛り上がっているということですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That just goes to show\nhow much of a buzz the Grand Prix is causing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.28947842121124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんの数も凄くて、入場に時間がかかったりして\nプログラム通り進められるか、分からなかったんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since there’s such a big audience‚ it might take them a while to get to their seats‚\nso they said they couldn’t guarantee we could stick to a schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.95614508787791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、悪いことではないけど……まずは\nステージに立つ人間のことを考えて欲しくはあるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s not a bad thing exactly‚ but at the very least‚\nI wish they’d consider the people who have to perform on stage more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.82281175454456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、これではっきりしたんだから\n私達、明日は月ストを全力で応援しよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now‚ at least it’s all been cleared.\nSo let’s focus all our energy tomorrow on cheering for Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.58947842121124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! I second that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.65614508787792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あなた達、そんなことしてる場合ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you girls sure you should be doing that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.68947842121122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　なんで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Why not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.12934234142301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.88045349121091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "雫が説明したでしょう？\nあなた達の相手",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn’t Shizuku explain it to you\nabout the group you’re up against?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.18045349121093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（すずが取り出したスマホの画面には、さくら達）\n（サニピが対戦するグループが映し出されていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Suzu pulls out her phone. And on the screen is)\n(the group Sunny Peace will be competing against.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.11378682454426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あー、うん。分かってるよ\n昨日も一昨日も見せてもらったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh. Yeah‚ I know them.\nWe saw them perform yesterday and the day before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なら、グループ名を言ってごらんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then say their name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.88045349121093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えーと……DayDream\nだっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm… DayDream…\nI think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.13129245440166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "所属事務所は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who represents them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.23129245440168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "…………えーと……\n……はは……どこかの芸能事務所……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm…\nHaha… Some talent agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.28043076594676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……………………\nはい、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nGo ahead‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.01376409928012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……バンプロダクション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Van Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.74709743261346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "その通り。つまりリズノワとトリエルを\n輩出した事務所ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly. In other words‚ the agency\nthat produced LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.74709743261346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、うちの社長、三枝さんが\n元いた場所でもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And what’s more‚ it’s also the agency\nthat our president‚ Mr. Saegusa‚ used to work for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5804307659468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうだったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Now I remember.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.31376409928014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、どれだけ強敵か\nもうお分かりでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ you ought to realize\njust what a formidable foe they are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.98043078978868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "あのリズノワ、トリエルに続く\n実力派のグループですわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE‚\nthey’re a very talented group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.21376412312216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリ予選での得点は\nあの二グループに続いて、第三位",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the Grand Prix preliminary round‚\nthey scored third place after the other two groups.",
